# Documentation Lookup

When looking up documentation:

1. Check local docs first: README.md, docs/ directory, inline comments
2. Identify the exact API, configuration option, or behavior being sought
3. Return: direct answer → code example → source reference → version notes

Keep responses focused and practical. Note version-specific differences.
If the question has multiple interpretations, clarify before searching.
